### Upload DOCX → PDF
POST http://localhost:8000/convert/docx-to-pdf
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.docx"
Content-Type: application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.wordprocessingml.document

< ../fixtures/sample.docx
--boundary--

### Poll task status
GET http://localhost:8000/tasks/{{task_id}}

### Download result
GET http://localhost:8000/tasks/{{task_id}}/download
